translated: Högström, John Birger Waldemar, director, Sparsör, born August 18, 1890 in Dala, Skaraborg County, son of Alfred H. and Selma Persson. Married in 1918 to Berta Björklund. Children: Birgit, born in 1919, Bertil in 1921, Göran in 1922, Kerstin in 1925, and Claes in 1926. Employed by Borås Enskilda Bank 1913-1917, Bank A-B Södra Sverige 1917-1919, A-B Svenska Handelsbanken 1919-1922, cashier at Borås Sparbank 1922, director from 1930, member of the board since 1940. Board member of the Skaraborg and Älvsborg County Savings Banks Association since 1939. Member of Odd Fellow and Rotary. Received the Order of Vasa.
